 S (收缩波)&amp;gt; D (舒张波)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Retrograde flow during ventricular systole&lt;br /&gt;
 心室收缩时出现逆向血流&lt;/p&gt;
