&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pulmonary outflow velocity spectrum obtained from a right parasternal right ventricular inflow-outflow view.&lt;br /&gt;
 从右胸骨旁右室流入 - 流出切面获得的肺流出速度频谱。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The peak velocity of the pulmonary flow (Vmax), the velocity time integral (VTI), the ejection time (ET), the time to peak velocity (TTP) and the pre-ejection period (PEP) of the pulmonary flow were measured as shown.&lt;br /&gt;
 测量肺血流峰值速度（Vmax）、速度 - 时间积分（VTI）、射血时间（ET）、峰值速度时间（TTP）和射血前时间（PEP），如图所示。&lt;/li&gt;
