&lt;h2 id=&#34;tapse-tricuspid-annular-plane-systolic-excursion-三尖瓣环平面收缩期偏移&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#tapse-tricuspid-annular-plane-systolic-excursion-三尖瓣环平面收缩期偏移&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; TAPSE (Tricuspid Annular Plane Systolic Excursion) 三尖瓣环平面收缩期偏移&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;gallery&#34;&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/11/iJyG8tbOnTaCj9W.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;Measurement of tricuspid annular plane systolic excursion&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
