 &lt;h1 id=&#34;coronary-arterial-anatomy&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#coronary-arterial-anatomy&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Coronary arterial anatomy&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;gallery&#34;&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://s2.loli.net/2022/07/05/4lsh3Y8wSyuozDZ.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
