&lt;h2 id=&#34;right-coronary-artery&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#right-coronary-artery&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Right coronary artery&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Arises from the right sinus of Valsalva, ies between pulmonary conus and right atrium&lt;br /&gt;
 发自右乏氏窦，位于动脉圆锥和右心房之间&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moves sharply towards left of the observer and is directed towards sternum&lt;br /&gt;
 快速向观察者左侧移动，并指向胸骨&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curves down following right AV groove in direction of acute margin of heart and diaphragm&lt;br /&gt;
 沿着右房室沟向心脏和横膈膜锐缘方向，向下弯曲&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curves posteriorly and follows AV groove towards crux cordis.&lt;br /&gt;
 沿着房室沟向心尖方向弯曲，向后弯曲&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;left-coronary-artery&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#left-coronary-artery&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Left coronary artery&lt;/h2&gt;
