&lt;h1 id=&#34;evaluation-of-the-atrial-volume&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#evaluation-of-the-atrial-volume&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Evaluation of the Atrial Volume&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Planimetry and dimensions combined&lt;br /&gt;
 平面测量和尺寸相结合&lt;/li&gt;
