&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/26/XL8zDWtViSAd9n4.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;Parasternal Long axis (PTLAX) 胸骨旁长轴&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
